                    "company": "Tijdschrift voor Mediageschiedenis (TMG)",
                    "description": "I have worked as one of the editors of Tijdschrift voor Mediageschiedenis, the Dutch academic forum for media history, regarding press history and the histories of film, radio and television, with a strong focus on the 20th and 21th centuries. Occasionally, we dedicate space to other media such as press photography and new media. It is possible to publish in English. As of 2012 the journal became an online journal. I co-edited special issues on Games & History (2004) and on Cinema Context (2006), a miscellanea issue in 2010, and a special issue on Madness & Media (2013). See also http://www.tmgonline.nl/index.php/tmg/index",
